    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>mini brioche rolls</strong> in half</p>\n<p>Add the <strong>bottom halves</strong> to a baking tray and put them in the oven for an initial 3-4 min or until starting to brown</p>\n<p>Tip: cooking them first stops the sliders from being soggy! </p>",
